DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,4,1);
$b = random(2,4,1);
$coef = $a;
$n = $a*$b*$b;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \($coef x^2-$n\). Your answer can be written as
\(A(x+B)(x+C)\) with integerss \(A\), \( B\), \(C\), and \(B<C \)
$BR where \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $a;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(C\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
